  <tr> 
    <td width="300" height="61">&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="400" height="61" bgcolor="#333333"> 
      <blockquote> 
        <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><strong><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br>
          <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="3">SAMUEL GOLDWYN'S 
          FILM</font></font></strong><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="3"><br />
          <br />
          <font size="4">The public had to wait for the first stereo recording 
          till 1959 when Samual Goldwyn's lengthy movie 'Porgy And Bess' was released, 
          starring Sidney Poitier and Dorothy Dandridge. The movie was very popular 
          and despite the criticism was an instant success, at least in the town 
          where I lived. </font></font><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="4"><br>
          </font> </font></p>
      </blockquote>
