      <p align="center"><img src="raponstageneg.jpg" width="250" height="229" alt=" "title="The earlist rap on stage."></p>
    </td>
    <td width="400" bgcolor="#333333" height="392"> 
      <blockquote> 
        <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><br>
          <font color="#FFCC00" size="4">I hates yo' struttin' style, <br>
          Yes sir, and yo' god damn silly smile<br>
          an' yo' ten cent di'mons an yo' fi'cent butts.<br>
          Oh, I hates yo' guts.</font></font></p>
        <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="4" color="#FFCC00">Somebody's 
          got to carve you up<br>
          to set these people free.<br>
          An' de writin' on de wall says<br>
          it's goin' to be me.</font></p>
        <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="4" color="#FFCC00">Some 
          night when you 's full of gin <br>
          and don't know I's about, <br>
          I'm goin' to take you by de tail<br>
          an' turn you inside out.</font></p>
